{"tid":1007831,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I] Fantasy life online [33] 話咁快又爆post，齊來吹水打去死去死活動","createTime":"2019-02-04T05:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T05:17:37.000Z","uid":131426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0edf5ba08344fec4c5ad9600374917a9754aece4","tid":1007831,"uid":131426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/004603_219d1804cc75a29b937e54371e5031bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F004603_219d1804cc75a29b937e54371e5031bc.png&h=5fd915b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/004604_219d1804cc75a29b937e54371e5031bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F004604_219d1804cc75a29b937e54371e5031bc.png&h=aa2cec12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n不負責宣言<br />\n以下有啲內容有機會過時，不過推post既巴打寧願每次解釋都懶得整理<br />\n所以盡量發問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n配信日    2018年7月23日<br />\n会社    Level5<br />\n<br />\nrpg <br />\n<br />\n最多4人合作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/004752_971bfbdf4889e1a51cf2f4edc766eb51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F004752_971bfbdf4889e1a51cf2f4edc766eb51.png&h=9b8c40da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可創造角色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/004827_1b8d517cdcbb170383e48e8085f4ddf4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F004827_1b8d517cdcbb170383e48e8085f4ddf4.png&h=bf918a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/004828_1b8d517cdcbb170383e48e8085f4ddf4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F004828_1b8d517cdcbb170383e48e8085f4ddf4.png&h=671cefb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n職業多種類<br />\n分普通，上級職業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/004930_86a93c18e1a027c03ddab9d985625d90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F004930_86a93c18e1a027c03ddab9d985625d90.png&h=33b2fb8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/004945_cc4a49f6830dc170f32ff2d9c7f66484.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F004945_cc4a49f6830dc170f32ff2d9c7f66484.png&h=0a643c73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抽蛋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/005025_862dd81329836f78e7305cfd8c12bfc3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F005025_862dd81329836f78e7305cfd8c12bfc3.png&h=b30381e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冒險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/005057_a5a31a380dfd6132dc5db6c894251057.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F005057_a5a31a380dfd6132dc5db6c894251057.png&h=079800cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/005058_dd9ec9993c9e4a753ff372b9417b7166.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F005058_dd9ec9993c9e4a753ff372b9417b7166.png&h=70188652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建築<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hJFjzju1XCM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhJFjzju1XCM&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=46f8e42a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hJFjzju1XCM</a><a href=\"https://youtu.be/hJFjzju1XCM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhJFjzju1XCM&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=46f8e42a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hJFjzju1XCM</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>Q&amp;A<br />\n</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 首刷刷咩好<br />\nA: 愈多五星愈好，有人抽到六粒五星，你自問有耐性刷到就俾心機刷啦<br />\n無一隻五星係無用既，你覺得佢廢全因為你唔識用佢<br />\n首抽建議上嚟問，排名經常變動，見到一堆負評就知你抽到好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點轉職<br />\nA: 主線打完1-2, 係地圖左面會出現職業神像, 兩個選項揀右邊<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點生產<br />\nA: 生產職業共5個, 成功轉職第一次會送相對應建築, 建築入面可以生產<br />\n<br />\nQ: 人物技能升邊種好<br />\nA: 由左至右, 基礎能力/攻擊段數/被動技能/主動技能, 請自行判斷, 個人戰鬥職業會先升主動技能<br />\n<br />\nQ: 日任係做啲乜柒<br />\nA: 上至下,討伐一次/探索一次/工作一次(係建築揀仕事)/耀日一次(即係打強化珠)/完成以上任務<br />\n<br />\nQ: 神之試練係咩?<br />\nA: 主線完咗之後，係星之庭園會出現新任務，做完送裝備<br />\n1. lvl 60以上大佬討伐<br />\n2. 每個職業故事完成或職業到達lvl60<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 職業主動技同武器主動技分別點開?<br />\nA: 職業技：長按後放手出技<br />\n武器技：長按儲氣之後加隨意一個方向放手<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有時迴避個陣會出技, 係咩玩法?<br />\nA: 代表你迴避傷害成功, 除咗碌地個陣無敵唔食傷之外, 仲獎你出招技而唔扣SP, 一般係對應人 <br />\n物連招最後個下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 釣魚咁難釣既，點玩架?<br />\nA: 釣魚跟佢方向拉: <br />\n<br />\n藍箭咀扣魚血, 魚線減耐久<br />\n<br />\n紅箭咀魚線回復耐久, 跟方向拉一下會show good, 之後放手, <br />\n唔好再拉, 拉又扣唔多魚血, 但魚線減耐久<br />\n<br />\n見到耐久回滿左又紅箭咀<br />\n可以儲下力, 放手 = 用角色技 / <br />\n儲力往外拉即刻放手 = 用武器技<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點先知幾時朝早，幾時夜晚?<br />\nA: <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/190730_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F190730_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=287941f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5af4336525ef48cdfd3fd5b43efab852ec9e96e","tid":1007831,"uid":131426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jces83w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJces83w.png&h=15a8ae84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【予告：本格始動！キャンペーン　＜1/23(水)から＞】<br />\n・ジェム最大1600個＋5万リッチ<br />\n・★5確定仲間召喚コイン<br />\n・★5確定装備召喚コイン<br />\n・スーパースターずきん　　全部もらえる！<br />\n「FLO今ログインすると超お得！本格始動キャンペーン」明後日から開催！<br />\n（映像の後半は大型アプデ1.2.00PVです）<br />\n<br />\n必中5星角色, 5星裝備, 44抽 (=1600石)<br />\n<br />\nPV:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/L5_fantasylife/status/1087276083882295296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FL5_fantasylife%2Fstatus%2F1087276083882295296&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=9306777d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FL5_fantasylife%2Fstatus%2F1087276083882295296&h=6f9f351e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/L5_fantasylife/status/1087276083882295296</a>"},{"pid":"1b04eb4cef3746fc8f8a13090ada222d53106a24","tid":1007831,"uid":131426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:08:17.000Z","msg":"Q: 回鍋一問，請問宜家隻驚究竟可以點玩?<br />\n<br />\nA:<br />\n想點玩就點玩<br />\n想追活動又得, 活動討伐, 釣魚活動<br />\n想日日斬下木掘下礦釣下魚又得<br />\n收集完材料去整下野又得<br />\n得閒打下金幣換下野又得<br />\n以上係廢話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">活動討伐</span><br />\n釣魚賺下exp珠, 藍板, 金鎖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">普通討伐</span> (太多時間就打埋)<br />\n20金=1金鎖 (每週1個)<br />\n10金=1藍板 (每週15個)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">裝備進化</span> (由EV1衝上EV20,  [EV10係百萬富翁保險線])<br />\n用藍板衝, 愈高EV用ge藍板愈多, 有機會大失敗降級<br />\n用埋金鎖就唔會降級, 但幾貴下, 不論你成功/失敗/大失敗, 都計你用左<br />\n一般ev16以上先開始用金鎖<br />\n<br />\nLV50,60,70 有新職任執照任務<br />\nLV70 = <span style=\"color: red;\">大師級</span>, 最多同時2個職係大師<br />\n每個職有一套大師裝[主角限定, 必須大師該職先著到]<br />\n另外大師有白靈材料打/採/制作<br />\n可以換主角限定[全職可用]大師裝"},{"pid":"453c57188e2e40c4c9d455d21b2e901b1b05814f","tid":1007831,"uid":131426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"裝備進化, 提升裝備能力, 有外觀轉變<br />\n型囉, 疊馬, 英雄主義<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.kekeke.cc/t/NpGCtLaHs1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.kekeke.cc%2Ft%2FNpGCtLaHs1.jpeg&h=ed5cd1ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好似咁, EV18!<br />\n<br />\n獨立職業限定大師裝<br />\n主角限定, 要大師該職業先著到<br />\n<br />\n例子: (伐木, 掘礦, 釣魚) <br />\n<img src=\"https://c.kekeke.cc/t/NpGLkkG9Vp.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc.kekeke.cc%2Ft%2FNpGLkkG9Vp.jpeg&h=e47caf7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n扮靚靚一流之餘, 仲會加能力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白靈材料先換到ge大師裝:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2sHaCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2sHaCe.jpg&h=47f4cea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所需白靈:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sLpROo6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLpROo6.png&h=324bafbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"229d9342f8a4a5fd3f2cb7d50d8d933430860680","tid":1007831,"uid":131426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:08:59.000Z","msg":"[quote]以下係巴哈轉載LINK<br />\n<br />\n巴哈討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/B.php?bsn=28200&amp;subbsn=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FB.php%3Fbsn%3D28200%26subbsn%3D0&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=51541874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/B.php?bsn=28200&amp;subbsn=0</a><br />\n<br />\n【討論】花形裝/大師裝/白靈裝 淺見 &amp; 大師套裝(5/12)效果增新中<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=28200&amp;snA=344&amp;tnum=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D28200%26snA%3D344%26tnum%3D1&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=95d545f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=28200&amp;snA=344&amp;tnum=1</a>"},{"pid":"e4fe2c79814e0879da3cd60bb5482d3d4d74f162","tid":1007831,"uid":131426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人一點半一齊打活動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打到夠數，預計連